ch.iserver.ace.net.core
Interface PortableDocumentExt

All Superinterfaces:
PortableDocument
All Known Implementing Classes:
PortableDocumentImpl
public interface PortableDocumentExt
extends PortableDocument

Interface extension of PortableDocument for the network layer. The added functionality concerns the creation of a portable document when parsing a document request.

See Also:
PortableDocument
